Original: <@RL,Boy2,03>電話 電話が あったんだ!<CD>ロボロボって やつらから!<CF><D1>兄さんを ヘルズゲ-トに<CD>おいて来たって!<CF><D1>早く! 早く 行かないと<CD>間に合わないよ!!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,06>だ だから その<CD>ヘルズゲ-トって 何なんだよ!?<CF><D1><@RL,Boy2,03>その名の通リ「じごくヘの門」だよ<CD>ヘブンスゲ-ト中から あつめられた<CF><D1>ゴミが そこで しょぶんされるんだ<CD>やつら ゲ-ムだって 言ってた!<CF><D1>つまリ 時間までに にっ兄さんを<CD>たすけられるか どうか!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,07>何だって!? あの ゆかいな<CD>イタズラしゅうだんが そっそんな<CF><D1>あくの そしきみたいなこと!<CD>どうなってんだ!?<CF><D1>とっとにかく それなら<CD>早く 大人の人を!<CF><D1><@RL,Boy2,03>それじゃ 間に合わない!<CD>大人は いっつも 行動が<CF><D1>おそいんだから!<CD>ぼく 1人だって 行くよ!
Translated: <@RL,Boy2,03>T-there was a call! From the RoboRobo Gang!<CF><D1>They left big bro in Hell's Gate!<CF><D1>Hurry! We need to hurry or we aren't gonna make it!!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,06>W-wait, what is Hell's Gate anyway!?<CF><D1><@RL,Boy2,03>It's where all the trash from Heaven's Gate is disposed of!<CF><D1>They even called it a game!<CF><D1>They want to see if we can save him in time!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,07>What!? That gang only knows how to pull off harmless pranks!<CF><D1>W-why did they suddenly become something like an evil organization!?<CF><D1>A-anyway, we should call the adults for help!<CF><D1><@RL,Boy2,03>They won't make it in time!<CF><D1>Adults are always so slow to act! I'll go by myself if I have to!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,07>まって! カモメちゃん!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,07>Gull! Wait!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>その ヘルズゲ-トって場所には<CD>ぼくが 行くよ!<CF><D1>カモメちゃんは 早く 大人の人を<CD>よんで来て!<CF><D1><@RL,Boy2,03>でもっ...!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>時間ないんだろ?<CD>だったら 早く!<CF><D1><@RL,Boy2,00>わ 分かった! じゃあ<CD>この カギを うけとって!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>I'll go to Hell's Gate or whatever that place is!<CF><D1>So Gull, you need to call the adults for help!<CF><D1><@RL,Boy2,03>But...!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>There's no time, right? Hurry up and go!<CF><D1><@RL,Boy2,00>G-got it! Then take this key with you!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>これは?<CF><D1><@RL,Boy2,00>ヘルズゲ-トは ヘブンスゲ-トの<CD>地下に あるんだ<CF><D1>エレベ-タ-で そのキ-を 使えば<CD>地下に 行けるようになる<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,04>カラスは ぼくが かならず たすける<CD>さあ カモメちゃん 早く 行って!<CF><D1><@RL,Boy2,00><&BUF0A>くん...<CF><D1>気をつけて!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,04>うん
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>What's this?<CF><D1><@RL,Boy2,00>Hell's Gate is in the basement of Heaven's Gate.<CF><D1>To go there, you need to use that key in the elevator.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,04>I'll save Crow, I promise! Now, go!<CF><D1><@RL,Boy2,00><&BUF0A>...<CF><D1>Be careful!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,04>Yeah.

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>ふうっ 何だか 大会どころじゃ<CD>なくなったな<CF><D1>宇宙リょこうを ゆめ貝て<CD>はじめた たたかいだったけど...<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,02>まってろよ! カラス!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00><f08>Sigh.<f00>.. This is no time for a tournament.<CF><D1>This all started when my dream to travel to space began...<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,02>Wait for me, Crow!

I can't enter Heaven's Tower.<CF><D1>Is there any other way for me to go inside?<CF><D1><@RL,Boy2,00>You can use my airbike!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,03>I can't ride one though. The airbike won't budge if there are two people on it!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,06>Then how...!?<CF><D1><@RL,Boy2,03>Oh, there's  my father's collection! He has <f02>Wings of Wind<f00>!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,06>Let's get going!

L-like I said, b-b-b-b-b-big bro is--!<CF><D1><@RL,Butter,00>Y-y-y-y-y-young master!?<CF><D1><@RL,Boy2,03>I mean my big bro!<CF><D1><@RL,Butter,00>My! Original: <@LL,Ikki,06>何で こんな時に!?<CD>ど どうしよう!

Translated: <@RL,Metabee,00>Hey!<CF><D1><@RL,Samantha,04>I feel my heart bursting open just by thinking about him.<CF><D1><@RL,Metabee,00>Hey, you! Can't you hear me!?<CF><D1><@RL,Samantha,04>What... You're so loud.<CF><D1>I don't feel like talking with a Medarot right now.<CF><D1><@RL,Metabee,00>I ain't got time for that!<CF><D1>Crow, as unpleasant as he is, is in a big pinch!<CF><D1><@RL,Samantha,04>If you find him unpleasant, then just leave him be.<CF><D1><@RL,Metabee,00>It's a different matter if his life is in danger!<CF><D1>I don't know how or why, but you and <&BUF0A>'s data got swapped!<CF><D1>So I have no other choice but to get you to help!<CF><D1><@RL,Samantha,04>Who died and made you boss?<CF><D1>And who's Crow anyway?<CF><D1><@RL,Metabee,00>He's the prime minister's son...<CF><D1>Oh yeah, I think he's also Gull's big brother.<CF><D1><@RL,Samantha,00>Hm~ 'That so?<CF><D1><@RL,Samantha,05>...!! Translated: <@RL,Rokusho,00>Hey.<CF><D1><@RL,Samantha,04>I feel my heart bursting open just by thinking of him.<CF><D1><@RL,Rokusho,00>Hey, you. Can you not hear me?<CF><D1><@RL,Samantha,04>What... You're so loud.<CF><D1>I don't feel like talking with a Medarot right now.<CF><D1><@RL,Rokusho,00>Your feelings do not matter at the moment.<CF><D1>There's a child named Crow who is in dire need of assistance.<CF><D1><@RL,Samantha,04>Who's that? Translated: <@RL,FemaleMedabot,00>My name isn't that vulgar, boss.<CF><D1><@LR,Samantha,03>Took you long enough.

Original: <@LL,Ikki,04>メダロッチの デ-タも<CD>元に もどったみたいだし!<CF><D1>行こう <&BUF07>!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,04>The Medarotch data has been restored back to normal!<CF><D1>Let's go, <&BUF07>!

Original: <@RL,Metabee,00>何が いやって また<CD>ここからって ところだよな<CF><D1>たまには お前が 転送されたら?
Translated: <@RL,Metabee,00>What I don't like is that I have to start all over again from here.<CF><D1>You should be the one who gets teleported for once.

Original: <@RL,Rokusho,00>ふん また ここからか<CD>たまには お前が<CF><D1>転送されたら どうだ?
Translated: <@RL,Rokusho,00>Hmph, here again?<CF><D1>How about you get teleported for once?

Original: <@RL,FlyingMedabot,00>ふ- 何にもないようで 何にもなくて<CD>何かあるようで 何かあリそうだよ<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,05>何言ってるか 分かんないし<CF><D1>キクヒメの デ-タとして むこうに<CD>行っちゃったかと 思ったよ
Translated: <@RL,FlyingMedabot,00>Phew... Seems like nothing, and it's nothing, seems like something, feels like something.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,05>What are you babbling about?<CF><D1>I thought you already went ahead as Kikuhime's data.

Original: <@RL,Spyke,00>どうしたんだ? <&BUF0A><CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,05>う うん いや...なんでもないよ
Translated: <@RL,Spyke,00>What's wrong, <&BUF0A>?<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,05>N-no... It's nothing.

Original: <@RL,Spyke,00>じゃ こいつを お前に<CD>あずけとくぜ!
Translated: <@RL,Spyke,00>Well, I'm give you this!

Original: <@RL,Topazia,03>こんどは.にがさ.ない!<CD>行く.わよ!
Translated: <@RL,Topazia,03>Next time. I won't. Let you. Pass! I'm. Leaving!

Original: <@RL,Topazia,03>ニンゲン.なんか.に!
Translated: <@RL,Topazia,03>The. Likes of. Human!

Original: <@RL,Samantha,00>ああ もう なんだか つかれたわぁ<CD>あんたに これ わたしとくわよぉ
Translated: <@RL,Samantha,00>Aah... I feel tired all of a sudden. I'll give this to you.

Original: <@RL,Samantha,00>先に 行っててよぉ
Translated: <@RL,Samantha,00>Just go already.

Original: <@RL,Spyke,04>あねご こんなとこ 早く出ましょう!
Translated: <@RL,Spyke,04>Boss, let's get out of here!

Original: <@RL,Sloan,03>あねご ぶじ...よかった...
Translated: <@RL,Sloan,03>Boss... Thank goodness... You're alright...

Original: カギが かかっている
Translated: It's locked.

Original: カギを はずした
Translated: It's unlocked.

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>こっちからは ひらかないようだ
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>It doesn't open from here.

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>ここから先も カ-ドキ-が<CD>いるかも知れないな
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>I might still need this card where I'm going.

Original: <@RL,Crow,00>ここに おちたら 空をとぶ のリもの<CD>でも ないかぎリ...<CF><D1>エアバイク 「風のつばさ」...<CF><D1>「風のつばさ」? このおれが<CD>あんな おもちゃに? フッ
Translated: <@RL,Crow,00>Without any flying vehicles, I can't afford to fall from here...<CF><D1>An airbike or... <f02>Wings of Wind<f00>...<CF><D1><f02>Wings of Wind<f00>? Heh, as if I would use that kind of toy.

Original: <@RL,Crow,00>あの 地上人が こわしたから すてた<CD>エアバイクか<CF><D1><@CC,CLEAR,FF>ガルルルル...
Translated: <@RL,Crow,00>This is the airbike that I threw away after that surface dweller broke it.<CF><D1><@CC,CLEAR,FF><f08>Grrrr<f00>...

Original: <@RL,MultiLeggedMedabot,00>右院 「おう! ここは 人間が<CD>来るところちゃうで!」<CF><D1>左院 「早ク 出テッテヨ-」<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,00>ふん どうやら おれが ピンチなのに<CD>気づいてないらしい
Translated: <@RL,MultiLeggedMedabot,00>Right Arm: "Hey! Humans shouldn't be in this place!"<CF><D1>Left Arm: "Hurry up and scram!"<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,00>Hmph, it seems he isn't aware that I'm in a pinch.

Original: <@RL,Crow,02>チィッ!!!
Translated: <@RL,Crow,02>Tsk!!!

Original: <@RL,Crow,02>くっ! 動けないっ!
Translated: <@RL,Crow,02>Ugh! I can't move!

Original: <@RL,Crow,00>おい そこのスイッチを おせ<CF><D1><@RL,MultiLeggedMedabot,00>頭 「ガルルルル」<CF><D1>右院 「早う かえれや コラァ!」<CF><D1>左院 「ソレジャ サヨナラ-!」
Translated: <@RL,Crow,00>Hey, press that button.<CF><D1><@RL,MultiLeggedMedabot,00>Head: "<f08>Grrrr!<f00>"<CF><D1>Right Arm: "Scram already!"<CF><D1>Left Arm: "Good bye now!"

Original: <@RL,Crow,00>くっ...あいつめ ねつで<CD>耳が いかれてやがるのか
Translated: <@RL,Crow,00>Ugh... Are his ears broken from all this heat?

Original: <@RL,Crow,00>...ゲ-ムオ-バ-か<CD>ふん おわらいだな
Translated: <@RL,Crow,00>...It's game over for me. Hmph, what a joke.

Original: <@RL,Crow,00>? 何をする?
Translated: <@RL,Crow,00>? What are you doing?

Original: <@RL,FloatingMedabot,00>このネツ 体に わるいデス<CF><D1>ワタシの 体の下に いれば<CD>少しは しのげマス
Translated: <@RL,FloatingMedabot,00>This heat is bad for your health.<CF><D1>It should get a little more bearable if you stay under me.

Original: <@RL,FemaleMedabot,00>わたしハ フィ-ルドを はリマス<CF><D1>少しデモ あなたノ やくに<CD>立てるナラ...
Translated: <@RL,FemaleMedabot,00>I'm putting up a field.<CF><D1>Anything that might alleviate your troubles.

Original: <@RL,TankMedabot,00>では ワタシは タテで<CD>ネツを ふせぎます<CF><D1>スラフシステムは こわれていますが<CD>技甲は 0では あリませんから
Translated: <@RL,TankMedabot,00>Then I'll use this shield to block the heat.<CF><D1>My Slough System may be broken, but my durability isn't 0.

Original: <@RL,Crow,00>「メダロット3げんそく」に<CD>しばられた<CF><D1>あわれな メダロットたちめ
Translated: <@RL,Crow,00>Poor Medarots. You're all bound by the <f02>Three Laws of Medarobotics<f00>.

Original: <@RL,FloatingMedabot,00>「メダロット3げんそく」に<CD>しばられてイル...カラじゃ<CF><D1>あリまセン...ワタシタチ<CD>人間を...マモリタイ
Translated: <@RL,FloatingMedabot,00>We're not doing this because of the <f02>Three Laws of Medarobotics<f00>...<CF><D1>It's because we... want to protect humans.

Original: <@RL,FemaleMedabot,00>ワタシタチ...人間...スキ<CD>あったかい...カラ<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,03>バカか お前らは!<CD>お前ら 人間に すてられたんだぞ!<CF><D1><@RL,TankMedabot,00>デモ...思い出...あったかい<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,02>バカが...つき合ってられん<CF><D1><@RL,TankMedabot,00>ウウアア!
Translated: <@RL,FemaleMedabot,00>We... love... humans... You... are... warm...<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,03>Are you guys stupid!? The ones who threw you away are humans!<CF><D1><@RL,TankMedabot,00>Still... the... memories... are... warm...<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,02>There's no saving your idiocy.<CF><D1><@RL,TankMedabot,00>Uuah!

Original: <@RL,FemaleMedabot,00>キャアア!
Translated: <@RL,FemaleMedabot,00>Eeek!

Original: <@RL,Crow,03>バカが! やめろ!<CD>しぬんだぞ! お前ら!<CF><D1><@RL,FloatingMedabot,00>「こわれる」ではなく「しぬ」デスカ<CF><D1>...うれしい アナタは さいごに<CD>ワタシタチを モノ ではなく<CF><D1>まるで 人間のように...<CD>生まれて来た かいが あリマ...
Translated: <@RL,Crow,03>Idiots! Stop it! You're gonna die!<CF><D1><@RL,FloatingMedabot,00>You didn't say 'break', but 'die'.<CF><D1>...We're so happy. In our last moments, you treat us as though we're humans, not just objects...<CF><D1>We're happy... to be born--

Original: <@RL,Crow,02>バカが...っ
Translated: <@RL,Crow,02>Idiots...!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,06>あかない!? こんな時に!<CF><D1>どこかに ドアを あける 何かが<CD>あると 思うんだけど...
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,06>It won't open! Why!?<CF><D1>There should be something that can open this door.

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>もう ここには 用はないよ<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,01>カラスも おちてないからね
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>There's nothing left to do here.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,01>Crow didn't fall down here after all.

Original: カ-ドキ-ヲ ゴテイジ シテ下サイ<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,06>これで ドアが ひらくのかな!?<CF><D1>カモメちゃんに もらったカ-ドキ-で<CD>だいじょうぶ かな?
Translated: <f02>Please present the keycard.<f00><CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,06>Is the door gonna open now!?<CF><D1>Is her keycard gonna work?

Original: <@LL,Ikki,01>動いた! この ボタンかな?
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,01>It moved! Is it this button?

Original: ツヅイテ 次ノ コンピュ-タ ヲ<CD>キドウ サセテ下サイ<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,06>まだなの!?
Translated: <f02>Please turn on the next computer.<f00><CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,06>There's still more!?

Original: ゲンザイ 入力マチ デス
Translated: <f02>Waiting for input.

Original: マダ 何カ 用?<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,05>ベつに 用はないよ
Translated: <f02>Need anything else?<CF><f00><D1><@LL,Ikki,05>Not really.

Original: デンゲン ガ 入ッテ オリマセン
Translated: <f08>There is no power.

Original: カ-ドキ-ヲ ゴテイジ シテ下サイ<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,06>は 早くしないと!
Translated: <f02>Please present the keycard.<f00><CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,06>I-I gotta hurry!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,01>動いた! この ボタンかな?
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,01>It moved! Is it this button?

Original: ツヅイテ 次ノ コンピュ-タ ヲ<CD>キドウ サセテ下サイ<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,06>いくつ あるんだよ!
Translated: <f02>Please turn on the next computer.<f00><CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,06>Just how many are there!?

Original: ゲンザイ 入力マチ デス
Translated: <f02>Waiting for input.

Original: デンゲン ガ 入ッテ オリマセン
Translated: <f02>There is no power.

Original: カ-ドキ-ヲ ゴテイジ シテ下サイ<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,06>いそがないと!
Translated: <f02>Please present the keycard.<f00><CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,06>I really need to hurry!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,01>動いた! この ボタンかな?
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,01>It moved! Is it this button?

Original: ツヅイテ 次ノ コンピュ-タ ヲ<CD>キドウ サセテ下サイ<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,07>そんな-! まだなの!?<CF><D1><@CC,CLEAR,FF>ウソ デスヨ ハッハッハ<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,06>.....
Translated: <f02>Please turn on the next computer.<f00><CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,07>No way! There's still more!?<CF><D1><@CC,CLEAR,FF>Just kidding. Hahaha.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,06>.....

Original: ゲンザイ ヘルズゲ-ト カイホウ中
Translated: <f02>Opening the Hell's Gate.

Original: <@LL,Ikki,02>あかない!? もうちょっとなのに!<CF><D1>近くに ドアを あける<CD>コンピュ-タが あるはずだ!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,02>It's not opening!? I was so close!<CF><D1>There must be a computer nearby that can open this door!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>このコンピュ-タは こわれている
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>This computer is out of order.

Original: <@LL,Ikki,07>あ! カ-ドキ-がっ!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,07>No! The keycard!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,02>かえせよ! それがないと カラスが!<CF><D1><@RL,Topazia,01>この子.たちに.勝てたら<CD>かえして.アゲ.ル
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,02>Give it back! I need that to save Crow!<CF><D1><@RL,Topazia,01>I will. Give it. Back. If you. Win Against. These. Children.

Original: <@LL,Ikki,02>早く かえせっ!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,02>Give it back, now!

Original: <@RL,Topazia,01>すてちゃえ
Translated: <@RL,Topazia,01>Throw it away.

Original: <@LL,Ikki,02>あっ! ずるいぞっ!<CF><D1><@RL,Topazia,01>ずるい?.どうして?<CF><D1>ニンゲンとの.やくそくは<CD>やぶるために.あるのよ.ネ!<CF><D1>あ.これ.オマケ
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,02>Hey! That's unfair!<CF><D1><@RL,Topazia,01>Unfair? How. So?<CF><D1>Promises. Made with. Humans. Are meant. To be. Broken!<CF><D1>Oh. Here is. Your. Bonus.

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>コンピュ-タが こわれたおかげで<CD>何とか 手でも あけられそうだ<CF><D1>キクヒメ もっと 力を 入れて!<CF><D1><@RL,Samantha,04>何よぉ あたしは 力しごとは<CD>きらいなんだからさぁ
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>Since the computer is broken, I think we'll have to force it open with our hands.<CF><D1>Kikuhime, put more strength to it!<CF><D1><@RL,Samantha,04>What... I hate doing physical labor!

Original: <@RL,Spyke,05>おい ちょっと まて!<CF><D1>そこを 勝手にあけたら<CD>お前も どうなるか 分からね-ぞ!<CF><D1>...って言うか あねごが!
Translated: <@RL,Spyke,05>Hey, stop!<CF><D1>We don't know what will happen to you if you try to open it like that!<CF><D1>...I mean, to Boss!

Original: <@RL,Samantha,02>いいから きょうリょくしな!<CF><D1>イワノイ!
Translated: <@RL,Samantha,02>We need a hand here!<CF><D1>Iwanoi!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,06>あかない!? どうしたら...<CF><D1><@RL,Spyke,04>こんなの むリだって
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,06>It won't open!? What now...<CF><D1><@RL,Spyke,04>This is just impossible.

Original: <@RL,Metabee,00><&BUF0A>! あれを 使うぜ!
Translated: <@RL,Metabee,00><&BUF0A>! Use that thing!

Original: <@RL,Rokusho,00><&BUF0A>! あれを 使うぞ!
Translated: <@RL,Rokusho,00><&BUF0A>! Use that thing!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,02>そうだ! さいごの 1つだけど...<CD>まよってる場合じゃ ない!<CF><D1>みんな はなれて!<CF><D1><@RL,Spyke,05>何する気だよぉ!<CF><D1><@RL,Samantha,02>いいから はなれなさいよぉ
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,02>That's right! It's the last one... But there's no time to hesitate!<CF><D1>Guys, step back!<CF><D1><@RL,Spyke,05>What are you gonna do!?<CF><D1><@RL,Samantha,02>Just step back already.

Original: <@LL,Ikki,01>やった-! ひらいた!<CF><D1><@RL,Sloan,03>ふくが よごれる-!<CF><D1><@RL,Spyke,01>ひゃ-! か-っこい-ぜ-!<CF><D1><@RL,Samantha,04>何よぉ さいきんは そんなのが<CD>はやってんのぉ?
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,01>Yeah! It's open!<CF><D1><@RL,Sloan,03>You got my clothes dirty!<CF><D1><@RL,Spyke,01>Whoo! That was so cool!<CF><D1><@RL,Samantha,04>What... Is that the latest fad?

Original: <@RL,Samantha,04>何よぉ こんな所に カラスってのが<CD>いるわけぇ?
Translated: <@RL,Samantha,04>What... Is Crow really in a place like this?

Original: <@RL,Spyke,04>あねご-! もう おさらば<CD>しましょうぜ こんな所!
Translated: <@RL,Spyke,04>Boss! Let's leave this place already!

Original: <@RL,Sloan,03>ふくが よごれちゃった...
Translated: <@RL,Sloan,03>My clothes got dirty...

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>このあなが ヘルズゲ-トに<CD>つづく ただ1つの 道なのか<CF><D1><@RL,Samantha,03>こわいのぉ?<CD><&BUF0A><CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>こわいよ でも 行かなくちゃ!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>The only way to get to Hell's Gate is through this hole.<CF><D1><@RL,Samantha,03><&BUF0A>, you scared?<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>Of course I am, but there's no other choice!

Original: <@RL,Topazia,01>くすくすっ.えいっ!
Translated: <@RL,Topazia,01>Hee hee. Take that!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,07>わあっ!!<CF><D1><@RL,Samantha,05>あっ!!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,07>Woah!!<CF><D1><@RL,Samantha,05>Ah!!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,05>いった-
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,05>Ouch...

Original: <@LL,Ikki,05>むぎゅ!<CF><D1><@RL,Samantha,04>あっついわね-<CD>何よ ここ
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,05>Nngh!<CF><D1><@RL,Samantha,04>It's so hot in here... What is this place?

Original: <@RL,Crow,00>「ヘルズゲ-ト」<CF><D1>しゃくねつの じごく<CD>天国の ゴミすて場だ
Translated: <@RL,Crow,00><f02>Hell's Gate, i<f00>t's the heaven's scrapyard, with a scorching heat akin to hell itself.

Original: <@LL,Ikki,01>カラス! ぶじだったのか!<CD>間に合って よかった!<CF><D1><@RL,Samantha,00>あんたが カラス?<CF><D1>カモメさまとは にても<CD>につかないわねぇ
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,01>Crow! You're alright! We made it in time!<CF><D1><@RL,Samantha,00>So you're Crow?<CF><D1>You look similar to my dear Gull, yet not at the same time.

Original: <@RL,Crow,00>地上人...なぜだ?<CD>なぜ ここに 来た?<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,04>何言ってんだ 当たリ前だろ?<CD>さあ 早くかえろう!<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,00>さっさと かえれ ここは もうすぐ<CD>人間の たえられない おんどまで<CF><D1>きおんが じょうしょう する<CF><D1>だい2は が 来たら いっかんの<CD>おわリだ みんな しぬ<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,06>だったら なおさら!<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,00>ダメだな おれは かえれない<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>えっ?<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,00>やつが あそこを まもって<CD>いるかぎリ<CF><D1><@RL,Samantha,02>ちょっと あんた 何言って...
Translated: <@RL,Crow,00>Surface dweller... Why? Why did you come here?<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,04>Don't be asking the obvious! Come on, let's get outta here!<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,00>You get out of here. The temperature will rise to the point humans won't survive.<CF><D1>When the second wave comes, it'll be the end for everyone here.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,06>Then let's hurry and go!<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,00>No, I can't go back.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>Eh?<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,00>Not when that guy is keeping watch.<CF><D1><@RL,Samantha,02>Hey, what are you saying--

Original: <@RL,Crow,03>来るな!
Translated: <@RL,Crow,03>Don't!

Original: <@RL,Samantha,05>うっ...何よぉ...これ...
Translated: <@RL,Samantha,05>Ugh... What... is this...

Original: <@LL,Ikki,07>キクヒメ!?
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,07>Kikuhime!?

Original: <@RL,Crow,00>近よるな ここには きょうれつな<CD>じゅうリょくが はたらいている<CF><D1>のがれられなくなるぞ<CF><D1>やつを たおして<CF><D1>スイッチでも おさない かぎリはな
Translated: <@RL,Crow,00>Stay away. There's a strong gravity field here.<CF><D1>Step one foot in and you won't be able to escape anymore.<CF><D1>That is, unless someone defeats him and presses the switch.

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>「やつ」って? あの スイッチが<CD>あるところに 出て来るの?
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>"Him"? Is he near the switch then?

Original: <@LL,Ikki,04>まかせといて!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,04>Just leave it to me!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,07>こ これは! ティンペットに<CD>「スカイカ-ゴ」の パ-ツが<CF><D1>ついたまま すてられてる
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,07>I-isn't this--! Someone threw this Tinpet away along with the <f02>Skycargo<f00> Part!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>まだ じゅうぶん 使えそうなのに<CD>どうして すてちゃうんだろうね
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>It still looks good. I wonder why they threw it away?

Original: <@LL,Ikki,03>スラフシステムも 作動 してない<CD>もう...動かないのかな...
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,03>The Slough System isn't running. I guess... he won't move anymore...

Original: <@RL,Crow,00>近よるな ここには きょうれつな<CD>じゅうリょくが はたらいている<CF><D1>のがれられなくなるぞ
Translated: <@RL,Crow,00>Stay away. There's a strong gravity field here.<CF><D1>Step one foot in and you won't be able to escape anymore.

Original: <@RL,MultiLeggedMedabot,00>頭 「ワンッ!」<CF><D1>右院 「おうっ! 何やワレェ!」<CF><D1>左院 「ナニモノ デ-ス!」<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,07>うわ! パ-ツがしゃベった!?<CD>まさか メダルが 3つも?<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,00>あのメダロットの 右院 左院<CD>パ-ツには スピ-カ-が<CF><D1>ついていて パ-ツが 勝手に<CD>しゃベっているように 貝えるだけだ
Translated: <@RL,MultiLeggedMedabot,00>Head: <f08>"Woof!"<f00><CF><D1>Right Arm: "Hey! Who are you!?"<CF><D1>Left Arm: "Who goes there!?"<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,07>Woah! The Parts can talk!? Does he have three Medals?<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,00>That Medarot has speakers in his Left and Right Arm Parts.<CF><D1>That's how he misleads people into thinking that way.

Original: <@LL,Ikki,04>ヘ- 何だかんだ 言っても やっぱリ<CD>カラスは メダロットがすきなんだね<CF><D1>ぼくも そこまでは 知らなかったよ<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,00>...ふん
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,04>I see. In the end, you love Medarots, don't you?<CF><D1>I didn't even notice until you pointed that out.<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,00>...Hmph.

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>ねえ きみ そこを<CD>どいてくれないかな?<CF><D1>友だちが あぶないんだ<CF><D1><@RL,MultiLeggedMedabot,00>頭 「ガルガルガル!」<CF><D1>右院 「あ? 何かうるっさいのぉ!」<CF><D1>左院 「ナ-ンデ-スカ-!?」<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>もしかして 耳が 聞こえないのか?<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,00>ねつで やられたんだろ<CF><D1>やつにとって おれたちは ただの<CD>しんにゅう者って ことだ<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>しかたないな
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>Hey, can you move aside?<CF><D1>My friend's in trouble.<CF><D1><@RL,MultiLeggedMedabot,00>Head: "<f08>Grr grr grr!<f00>"<CF><D1>Right Arm: "Huh? Shut yer trap!"<CF><D1>Left Arm: "What did you say!?"<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>Are his ears not working?<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,00>They must be broken from the heat.<CF><D1>We're no more than intruders in his eyes.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>No other choice then.

Original: <@RL,MultiLeggedMedabot,00>頭 「キャイン キャイン」<CF><D1>右院 「イタッ 何すんねん!?」<CF><D1>左院 「ボウリョクハ イケナ-イ!」
Translated: <@RL,MultiLeggedMedabot,00>Head:<f09> Whimper whimper...<f00><CF><D1>Right Arm: "Ow! What's yer problem!?"<CF><D1>Left Arm: "Say no to violence!"

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>スイッチがある<CF><D1>このスイッチを おそうかな?<*04>
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>There's a switch here.<CF><D1>Should I press it?<*04>

Original: <@LL,Ikki,06>な 何が おこるんだ?
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,06>W-what's happening?

Original: <@LL,Ikki,04>これかな?
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,04>Is it this one?

Original: <@RL,Samantha,05>あら? 体が じゆうに なったわぁ
Translated: <@RL,Samantha,05>Oh? I can move now.

Original: <@LL,Ikki,07>な 何が おこるんだ?
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,07>W-what's happening?

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>何の はんのうも ない
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>Nothing happened.

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>やっぱリ やめておこう
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>Never mind.

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>この メダロットたちは?<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,00>すくいようのない バカどもだ<CD>おれを まもって しにやがった<CF><D1><@RL,Samantha,02>ちょっと あんたねぇ!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>キクヒメ! 手つだって!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>What happened to these Medarots?<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,00>They're a helpless bunch of idiots who wasted their lives to protect me.<CF><D1><@RL,Samantha,02>Hey, that's not nice!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>Kikuhime! Lend me a hand!

Original: <@RL,Samantha,00>はぁ?
Translated: <@RL,Samantha,00>Huh?

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>これを こうして...っ!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>Here... And here!

Original: <@RL,Crow,00>何をしている?<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>メダロットから メダルを<CD>ぬいてるんだ<CF><D1>メダロットはかせなら<CD>もしかしたら 直せるかもしれない<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,00>バカな そんなことをしても<CD>むいみだ こいつらは もう...
Translated: <@RL,Crow,00>What are you doing?<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>I'm taking their Medals out.<CF><D1>Dr. Medarot might be able to fix them.<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,00>Idiot. What point is there? These guys are no longer...

Original: <@LL,Ikki,04>なかないで カラス<CF><D1>きっと だいじょうぶだから<CD>あきらめないで きみも てつだって<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,03>ないて? おれが? バカな...<CD>いつの間に...<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,04>よかった カモメちゃん<CD>しんぱいしてたから<CF><D1>カラスから なみだが<CD>きえたんじゃないかってさ<CF><D1>...さあ がんばろう!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,04>Crow, don't cry.<CF><D1>It's all gonna be okay, so don't give up hope. Help me out here.<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,03>Cry? Me? This can't be... Since when...<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,04>Thank goodness. Gull's been worried about you.<CF><D1>She thought your tears have all dried away.<CF><D1>...Alright, let's do this!

Original: <@RL,Spyke,05>あねご--っ!!
Translated: <@RL,Spyke,05>Booooss!!

Original: <@RL,Sloan,03>イ イタイ...
Translated: <@RL,Sloan,03>O-ow...

Original: <@RL,Spyke,01>よかった! あねご<CD>ぶじだったんですね!
Translated: <@RL,Spyke,01>Thank goodness! Boss, you're alright!

Original: <@RL,Samantha,00>あんたたちも てつだいなさぁい<CF><D1><@RL,Spyke,00>ヘ? 何を?<CF><D1><@RL,Samantha,00>こわれた メダロットたちから<CD>メダルを ぬくのよぉ
Translated: <@RL,Samantha,00>Help us out here.<CF><D1><@RL,Spyke,00>Huh? With what?<CF><D1><@RL,Samantha,00>Remove the Medals from all these broken Medarots.

Original: <@RL,Crow,00>だが どうやって<CD>ここから 出るつもリだ?
Translated: <@RL,Crow,00>Still, how are we gonna get out of here?

Original: <@LL,Ikki,04>「風のつばさ」が あるじゃないか<CF><D1>これにのれば 上のかいまで<CD>いっきに 行けるよ<CF><D1>まずは カラスからだ<CD>ほら のって!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,04>By using <f02>Wings of Wind<f00>, of course.<CF><D1>With this, we can head to the upper floor in one foul swoop.<CF><D1>You go first, Crow. Get on!

Original: <@RL,Crow,00>そんな おもちゃに のる気は ない
Translated: <@RL,Crow,00>I'm not riding that toy.

Original: <@LL,Ikki,02>そんなこと 言ってる場合じゃ...<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,06>しまった! パ-ツがない!?<CD>だれか 持ってない?<CF><D1><@RL,Samantha,00>そんなの 知らないわよぉ<CF><D1><@RL,Spyke,05>おれも 持ってないぞ!<CF><D1><@RL,Sloan,03>ボクも 持ってない...<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,00>みんな まとめて くたばるだけだ<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>カラス ここを だっしゅつする時は<CD>きみが 1番 さいしょだよ<CF><D1>きみが にげないと ぼくらも<CD>にげられないからね<CF><D1><@RL,Spyke,05>ちょ ちょっとまてよ! そんなやつ<CD>ほっといて にげようぜ!<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,00>それがいい おれは たすけろなんて<CD>たのんだ おぼえは ない<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>...とにかく 使えそうなものを<CD>さがすから いいね?
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,02>This isn't the time to be picky...<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,06>Oh no! I don't have the Parts!? Does anyone have it?<CF><D1><@RL,Samantha,00>Don't ask me.<CF><D1><@RL,Spyke,05>I don't have it, either!<CF><D1><@RL,Sloan,03>Me neither...<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,00>So we're all dying here.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>Crow, when we get our ticket to escape, you'll be the first one to go.<CF><D1>Otherwise, we won't be able to leave either.<CF><D1><@RL,Spyke,05>W-wait a sec! Just forget about him and get us the hell outta here!<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,00>Agreed. I never asked for your help to begin with.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>...Anyway, let's search for something we can use.

Original: <@LL,Ikki,05>しまった パ-ツを 租んでない!<CD>すぐに 租み立てよう!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>カラス 言っとくけど きみが<CD>1番に だっしゅつするんだからね<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,00>ふん!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,05>Oh no, the Parts aren't assembled! Let' assemble them right away!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>Crow, I'll say this again. You'll be the first one to leave.<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,00>Hmph!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,04>そんなこと 言わないでさ<CD>これで 上に あがれるよ!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,04>Don't say that. This will bring us to the upper floor!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,04>さあ のって!<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,00>にげたければ 自分たちだけで<CD>にげれば いい...<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>メダルを たすけたく ないの?<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,00>.....<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>分かってるとは 思うけど<CF><D1>今は えリごのみしてる<CD>場合じゃないんだからね<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,04>さ! 早く!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,04>Get on!<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,00>Just go by yourselves.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>Don't you want to save those Medals?<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,00>.....<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>I know you realize this already, but this is no time to be picky.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,04>Go! Hurry!

Original: <@RL,Samantha,03>じゃ そういう ことで あたしたちも<CD>上に あがらせて もらうわよぉ
Translated: <@RL,Samantha,03>Well then, it's our turn to go up.

Original: <@RL,Samantha,04>じゅうリょう オ-バ- みたいねぇ<CD>イワノイ あんた おリてよぉ<CF><D1><@RL,Spyke,05>あねご! それなら カガミヤマ...
Translated: <@RL,Samantha,04>Seems like we're over capacity. Iwanoi, get off.<CF><D1><@RL,Spyke,05>Boss! Then what if Kagamiyama--

Original: <@RL,Samantha,03>まってるからさぁ 早く来なさいよぉ!<CF><D1><@RL,Spyke,04>そ そんなぁ<CF><D1><@RL,Spyke,02>よ ようし こうなったら!
Translated: <@RL,Samantha,03>We're waiting! Hurry up and get here!<CF><D1><@RL,Spyke,04>N-no way!<CF><D1><@RL,Spyke,02>F-fine, in that case!

Original: <@RL,Spyke,03>今こそ 新しく 生まれ変わった<CD>お前の 力を みせる時だ!<CF><D1><@RL,BipedMedabot,00>まかせて下さい おやびん!<CD>さあ のって!
Translated: <@RL,Spyke,03>It's time for your new power to shine!<CF><D1><@RL,BipedMedabot,00>Leave it to me, boss! Get on!

Original: <@RL,Spyke,04>にきゃく じゃ ねぇ...<CF><D1><@RL,BipedMedabot,00>にきゃく ですから ねぇ...
Translated: <@RL,Spyke,04>You're not... bipedal...<CF><D1><@RL,BipedMedabot,00>I'm not bipedal, after all...

Original: <@LL,Ikki,04>さあ ぼくも 早く上がらないと
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,04>Now it's my turn to go up.

Original: <@RL,Topazia,03>ニ.ン.ゲ.ン!<CD>にがさ.ない!
Translated: <@RL,Topazia,03>Hu. Man! You're not. Getting. Away!

Original: <@RL,Topazia,03>もっと.あそび.たかった.の...に
Translated: <@RL,Topazia,03>I still. Want to. Play...

Original: <@LL,Ikki,07>ポケットが あたたかい...<CD>また 6負かヘい石に 絵が!?
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,07>My pocket feels warm... Is the 6-Sided Nummulite doing it again!?

Original: <@LL,Ikki,06>うわ-! すごく あつくなってきたぞ<CD>早く だっしゅつしなくちゃ!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,06>Woah! I gotta hurry!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,04>大会 もう おわっちゃっただろうな<CD>あ-あ
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,04>I bet the tournament's already over. <f02>Sigh<f00>...

Original: <@RL,Boy2,01>よかった...兄さん<CD>ぶじで 本当に よかった...<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,00>...ああ しんぱい かけたな
Translated: <@RL,Boy2,01>Big bro... You're safe... Thank goodness... Truly...<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,00>...Yeah, sorry for making you worry.

Original: <@RL,Metabee,00>いもうとには やさしいんだな<CF><D1><@RL,Samantha,03>ああ お兄さま 思いの<CD>カモメさま すてきだわぁ♥
Translated: <@RL,Metabee,00>You're only kind to your own sister, eh?<CF><D1><@RL,Samantha,03>Aww... My dear Gull's affection towards his big brother is so lovely~♥

Original: <@RL,Rokusho,00>いもうとには やさしいのだな<CF><D1><@RL,Samantha,03>ああ お兄さま 思いの<CD>カモメさま すてきだわぁ♥
Translated: <@RL,Rokusho,00>The only one you show affection to your own sister, huh.<CF><D1><@RL,Samantha,03>Aww... My dear Gull's affection towards his big brother is so lovely~♥

Original: <@RL,Samantha,05>えぇっ!!<CD>い いもうとぉ!?<CF><D1><@RL,Metabee,00>あれ? 言ってなかったっけ?
Translated: <@RL,Samantha,05>Eeh!? S-sister!?<CF><D1><@RL,Metabee,00>Huh? Did I never tell you?

Original: <@RL,Samantha,05>えぇっ!!<CD>い いもうとぉ!?<CF><D1><@RL,Rokusho,00>知らなかったのか?
Translated: <@RL,Samantha,05>Eeh!? S-sister!?<CF><D1><@RL,Rokusho,00>You didn't know?

Original: <@RL,Samantha,05>う...うそぉ...
Translated: <@RL,Samantha,05>N-no way...

Original: <@RL,Samantha,04>.....
Translated: <@RL,Samantha,04>.....

Original: <@RL,Spyke,05>あねご!
Translated: <@RL,Spyke,05>Boss!

Original: <@RL,Sloan,01>ドンマイ!
Translated: <@RL,Sloan,01>Don't worry about it!

Original: <@RL,Crow,00>なぜ たすけた?<CF><D1>おれは お前たちを...
Translated: <@RL,Crow,00>Why did you save me?<CF><D1>After all the things I did...

Original: <@LL,Ikki,04>いいんだよ カラス そんなこと<CD>でも 本当に ほっとしたよ
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,04>Crow, don't worry about it. Everything's fine. Still, I feel so relieved.

Original: <@RL,Man,00>本当に 何と おれいを<CD>言っていいものか...<CF><D1>カラスは やっかいな<CD>ひねくれものだが<CF><D1>これでも わたしの<CD>大切な むすこだ<CF><D1>わたしに できることなら<CD>何でも しよう<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>そうですね...じゃあ<CF><D1>ヘルズゲ-トに メダロットを<CD>すてるのは もう やめてください!<CF><D1><@RL,Man,00>はて? それはまた 変わった<CD>のぞみだな どういうことだね?<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>メダロットは ものじゃないんです!<CD>かぞくや 友だちを<CF><D1>「動けなくなった」って リゆうで<CD>ゴミばこに すてますか?<CF><D1>この町の人たちは それと同じことを<CD>してるんです!<CF><D1><@RL,Butter,00>これ! そうリに なまいきな 口を!
Translated: <@RL,Man,00>Truly, I don't know how to thank you...<CF><D1>Crow is a troublesome fellow who's bad with his words.<CF><D1>But even so, he's still my precious son.<CF><D1>I'll grant you anything want as long as it's within my capabilities.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>Let me think...<CF><D1>I want people to stop throwing away Medarots into Hell's Gate!<CF><D1><@RL,Man,00>Hm? That's an odd request. Why do you want that?<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>Medarots aren't just objects!<CF><D1>If your family members or your friends <f02>stop moving<f00> one day, will you throw them into the trash can?<CF><D1>That's what the people in this town are doing to their Medarots!<CF><D1><@RL,Butter,00>Hey! Mind what you say to the prime minister!

Original: <@RL,Man,00>トンビ だまっていろ!<CF><D1><@RL,Butter,00>もっ もうしわけあリません
Translated: <@RL,Man,00>Shut up, Tonbi!<CF><D1><@RL,Butter,00>M-my apologies.

Original: <@RL,Man,00>お前も そう思うか? カラス<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,00>あいつらが すてられて いなければ<CD>おれは たすからなかったな<CF><D1><@RL,Man,00>どういう いみだ?<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,04>カラスは メダロットたちに<CD>たすけられたんです<CF><D1>本当の いのちの おんじんは<CD>ヘルズゲ-トに すてられて <CF><D1>ほとんど 動けなくなっていた<CD>メダロットたちなんです!<CF><D1><@RL,Man,00>...なるほど この ひねくれ者め<CD>すなおに おれいも 言えんのだな<CF><D1>分かったよ <&BUF0A>くん<CD>大切な ことを<CF><D1>きみたちに おしえられた<CD>もう この町で メダロットが<CF><D1>すてられることは ない<CD>心を なくしていたのは<CF><D1>メダロットではなく<CD>人間の方だったのだな<CF><D1>とリあえず 今は 休むがいい<CD>あとには 大会が まっている<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,07>えっ! 大会は おわったんじゃあ!<CF><D1><@RL,Man,00>メインメンバ-が かけて<CD>大会が 行われるわけはない<CF><D1>きみには すばらしい ロボトルを<CD>きたい しているよ
Translated: <@RL,Man,00>Crow, do you agree with what he's saying?<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,00>If they weren't thrown in there, I wouldn't be standing here now.<CF><D1><@RL,Man,00>What do you mean?<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,04>Crow was saved by the Medarots that were thrown in there.<CF><D1>They're the ones who truly saved his life...<CF><D1>After they were thrown into Hell's Gate... they could barely move!<CF><D1><@RL,Man,00>...I see. So you can't even display your feelings of gratitude properly.<CF><D1>I understand, <&BUF0A>. You've taught me something important.<CF><D1>No Medarots in this town shall ever be thrown away again.<CF><D1>The ones who have lost their hearts aren't Medarots, but us humans.<CF><D1>Get some rest for now. You still have a tournament to attend.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,07>Eh!? Isn't it over already?<CF><D1><@RL,Man,00>There's no way a tournament can proceed without the main participants.<CF><D1>I'm looking forward to your magnificent robattles.

Original: <@LL,Ikki,04>ぼくも この メダルを しゅうリして<CD>もらいに メダロットはかせの<CF><D1>所に 行こう!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,04>I should go see Dr. Medarot so he can fix these Medals!

Original: <@RL,Samantha,02>ちょっとぉ どうにかしてよぉ
Translated: <@RL,Samantha,02>Hey... Do something about this.

Original: <@RL,Samantha,03>おれいは 言わないわよぉ
Translated: <@RL,Samantha,03>Don't expect a thank you.

Original: <@RL,Spyke,04>早く こんな所 おさらば しようぜ
Translated: <@RL,Spyke,04>Let's say goodbye to this place.

Original: <@RL,Sloan,03>ううう ゴミだらけ
Translated: <@RL,Sloan,03>Uuh... There's trash everywhere.

Original: <@RL,Samantha,02>ちょっとぉ しっかリしなさいよぉ!
Translated: <@RL,Samantha,02>Hey... Straighten up!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,06>あ! ロボロボ団!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,06>Ah! It's the RoboRobo Gang!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,02>こんな所で 何してるんだ!<CF><D1><@RL,RubberRoboGrunt,03>ここで さぼってたら オレだけ<CD>おいていかれたロボ<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,05>それは「じごうじとく」ってやつだろ?<CF><D1><@RL,RubberRoboGrunt,03>ロボ-<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,02>とリあえず セレクトしぶに<CD>つれて行くからな!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,02>What are you doing here!?<CF><D1><@RL,RubberRoboGrunt,03>I was goofing off around here, then I got left behind, robo.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,05>That's what' you call getting your <f02>Just Deserts.<f00><CF><D1><@RL,RubberRoboGrunt,03>Robo...<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,02>Anyway, I'm taking you to the Select Corp Branch!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>ロボロボ団を セレクトしぶに<CD>つれて行こう たしか オフィス1だ
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>I should take the RoboRobo Gang member to the Select Corp Branch. I think it's in office 1.

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>何?<CF><D1><@RL,RubberRoboGrunt,01>エレベ-タ-の ボタンは おれが<CD>おしてやるロボ!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>What?<CF><D1><@RL,RubberRoboGrunt,01>I'll press the elevator buttons for you, robo!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,06>あああ! エレベ-タ-の ボタンが<CD>全部 おされている! 何てことだ!<CF><D1><@RL,RubberRoboGrunt,01>ふっふっふ おそろしいロボか?<CD>これが われわれの やリ方ロボ!<CF><D1>次は ホテルの インタ-ホンを<CD>おして にげるロボよ-!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,06>Aaah! You pressed all of them! What are you doing!?<CF><D1><@RL,RubberRoboGrunt,01>Hee hee! Terrified, robo? This is our way of doing things, robo!<CF><D1>Next, I'll ding dong ditch the interphones in the hotel, robo!

Original: <@RL,RubberRoboGrunt,01>さらばロボ!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,06>ま まて!
Translated: <@RL,RubberRoboGrunt,01>Farewell, robo!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,06>W-wait!

Original: <@RL,RubberRoboGrunt,00>おれは 人形だロボ
Translated: <@RL,RubberRoboGrunt,00>I'm a doll, robo.

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>いや ロボロボ団だよね<CF><D1><@RL,RubberRoboGrunt,00>ちがうロボ<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>いや ちがわないよね<CF><D1><@RL,RubberRoboGrunt,03>ほ ほんとに ちがうロボよ!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,01>じゃ セレクト隊に もって行こう<CF><D1><@RL,RubberRoboGrunt,02>お お前を たおして にげるロボ!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>No, you're from the RoboRobo Gang.<CF><D1><@RL,RubberRoboGrunt,00>I'm not, robo.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>Yes, you are.<CF><D1><@RL,RubberRoboGrunt,03>I-I'm really not, robo!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,01>I should take you to the Select Corp then.<CF><D1><@RL,RubberRoboGrunt,02>I-I'll defeat you and make my getaway, robo!

Original: <@RL,RubberRoboGrunt,03>さらばロボ-!
Translated: <@RL,RubberRoboGrunt,03>Farewell, robo!

Original: <@RL,RubberRoboGrunt,04>ロボ!<CF><D1><@RL,SelectCorpsGrunt,02>おとなしくするで あリます!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,01>わるいことは できないよね
Translated: <@RL,RubberRoboGrunt,04>Robo!<CF><D1><@RL,SelectCorpsGrunt,02>Stop resisting!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,01>You can't do bad things.

Original: <@LL,Ikki,07>ここ これは! メダルだ!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,07>T-t-this is... A Medal!

Original: <@RL,Butter,00>何用ですかな?<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>メダロットはかせ 来てませんか?<CF><D1><@RL,Butter,00>はかせなら 2Fに いらっしゃいます
Translated: <@RL,Butter,00>What do you need?<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>Is Dr. Medarot here?<CF><D1><@RL,Butter,00>Yes, he is on 2F.

Original: <@RL,Butter,00>ユウキぼっちゃまは<CD>おるすで ございます
Translated: <@RL,Butter,00>Young master Yuki is away at the moment.

Original: <@RL,FemaleMedabot,00>つまみ食いは だめですよ
Translated: <@RL,FemaleMedabot,00>No eating snacks~

Original: <@RL,FemaleMedabot,00>テ-ブル ふきましょ フ-キフキ♪
Translated: <@RL,FemaleMedabot,00>Time to wipe the table~ Wipe wipe~♪

Original: <@RL,FemaleMedabot,00>テ-ブル ふいて キュッキュッキュ♪
Translated: <@RL,FemaleMedabot,00>Wiping the table~ Squeak squeak squeak~♪

Original: <@RL,FemaleMedabot,00>女型メダロットが 多いのは<CD>ぼっちゃんの しゅみよ
Translated: <@RL,FemaleMedabot,00>The reason why there are so many female Medarots is due to young master's preferences.

Original: <@RL,FemaleMedabot,00>お茶でも どうですか?
Translated: <@RL,FemaleMedabot,00>Would you like some tea?

Original: <@RL,FemaleMedabot,00>ワタシも この「レディブ-スタ-」の<CD>パ-ツをつけて 空を とびたいわ<CF><D1>むかしは ひこう型メダロットと言えば<CD>女型メダロットの 花形だったのにね
Translated: <@RL,FemaleMedabot,00>I'd like to put on this <f02>Ladybooster<f00> Part and soar into the skies.<CF><D1>Flying-types used to be the favored type for female Medarots.

Original: <@RL,Lady,00>何なのさ? ここは メダロット社<CD>ニモウサク社長の 家だよ<CF><D1>ぼうやが 来るところじゃ ないんだよ
Translated: <@RL,Lady,00>What is it? This residence belongs to Nimosaku, the Medarot Company's president.<CF><D1>You shouldn't be loitering around here.

Original: <@RL,Lady,00>ユウキぼっちゃんの しゅみは<CD>むかしから ちっとも 変わんないね
Translated: <@RL,Lady,00>The young master's tastes haven't changed for as long as I can remember.

Original: <@LL,Ikki,04>あ! これは レディブ-スタ-だ!<CF><D1>前は こいつに「風のつばさ」を<CD>つけてたんだ なつかしいなぁ
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,04>Ah! It's Ladybooster!<CF><D1>I remember attaching <f02>Wings of Wind<f00> to it before. This really brings me back.

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>うわ! 「サル」メダルだ<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,04>イワノイは この かくとうに むいた<CD>メダルを しゃげきメダロットに<CF><D1>入れていたんだよなぁ
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>Woah! It's the <f02>Monkey<f00> Medal! <CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,04>Even though this Medal is suited for grappling, Iwanoi put it in a Shooting Medarot instead.

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>これは 「ト-タス」メダルだ<CF><D1>こうがくパ-ツと あいしょうが<CD>合ってる メダルだったな
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>This is the <f02>Tortoise<f00> Medal.<CF><D1>I remember it being compatible with Optical Parts.

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>これは 6かくかヘい石 みたいだ<CD>ぼろぼろ だから よく 分からない
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>This one looks like the 6-Sided Nummulite, but it's too worn out for me to tell for sure.

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>このメダルは われていて しゅるいが<CD>よく 分からない
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>Because this Medal is cracked, I've got no clue about what kind it is.

Original: <@RL,Nae,01>どうしたのですか?<CD><&BUF0A>くん<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,03>じつは...<CF><D1><@RL,Nae,02>まあ それは大変ですわ<CD>でも おじいさまなら...
Translated: <@RL,Nae,01>What's wrong, <&BUF0A>?<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,03>Actually...<CF><D1><@RL,Nae,02>My, that sounds terrible. But I'm sure grandfather will be able to handle it.

Original: <@RL,Nae,01>わたしたちは メダル<CD><&BUF0A>くんは 大会<CF><D1>今は 自分に できることを<CD>全力で なしとげましょう<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,04>分かリました ぼく がんばリます!
Translated: <@RL,Nae,01>We'll take care of the Medals. You should focus on the tournament.<CF><D1>Give it your best on what you can actually do.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,04>I understand. I will give it my all!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,06>はかせ!<CF><D1><@RL,DrAki,00>どうしたんじゃ? <&BUF0A><CD>そんなに いきを 切らして<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,06>これを! こわれた メダルを<CF><D1>貝てもらいたいんです!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,06>Professor!<CF><D1><@RL,DrAki,00>What's wrong, <&BUF0A>? You're out of breath.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,06>Please have a look at these broken Medals!

Original: <@RL,DrAki,00>ほお これは また...<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,06>はかせ! メダルたちは<CD>たすかリそうですか?<CF><D1><@RL,DrAki,00>ふむ...なかなか<CD>やっかいじゃわい<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,06>はかせ!<CF><D1><@RL,DrAki,01>「やっかい」じゃが「できん」とは<CD>言うとらん<CF><D1>わしを だれだと 思っとる!<CD>わしは...
Translated: <@RL,DrAki,00>My... These are quite...<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,06>Professor! Can you save these Medals?<CF><D1><@RL,DrAki,00>Hm... It won't be an easy task.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,06>Professor!<CF><D1><@RL,DrAki,01>I said it <f02>wasn't easy<f00>. I didn't say It's impossible, right?<CF><D1>Who do you think I am? I'm none other than--

Original: <@RL,Nae,01>「メダロットの けんい<CD>メダロットはかせじゃ!」ですか?<CF><D1><@RL,DrAki,03>先に 言うでないっ!
Translated: <@RL,Nae,01>"The Medarot Expert, Dr. Medarot!" ...Is that it?<CF><D1><@RL,DrAki,03>Don't steal my words!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,01>あはは!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,04>じゃあ はかせ おねがいします!<CF><D1>それが 直らないと 友だちが<CD>かなしむんです<CF><D1><@RL,DrAki,01>うむうむ まかすがいい
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,01>Ahaha!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,04>Professor, I'm leaving them in your care!<CF><D1>My friend would be sad if he heard that you couldn't fix them.<CF><D1><@RL,DrAki,01>Mm-hmm! Leave it to me.

Original: <@RL,DrAki,01>しんぱい するな メダルは かならず<CD>直してやるわい!
Translated: <@RL,DrAki,01>Don't worry, I'll fix the Medals right back up!

Original: <@RL,Samantha,04>はああ ふこうよねぇ<CF><D1>あいてが 女とも 知らず<CD>ひと目ぼれした あたしって...
Translated: <@RL,Samantha,04><f08>Sigh..<f00>. What luck...<CF><D1>I fell in love with someone who turned out to be a girl all along...

Original: <@RL,Samantha,04>イワノイといい カガミヤマといい<CF><D1>どぉして あたしは こう<CD>男うんが ないのかしらねぇ<CF><D1><@RL,Spyke,04>そんなぁ あねごぉ
Translated: <@RL,Samantha,04>First there's Iwanoi, then Kagamiyama...<CF><D1>Why do I have no luck when it comes to finding a man?<CF><D1><@RL,Spyke,04>Boss... That's not nice...

Original: <@RL,Sloan,01>ドンマイ!
Translated: <@RL,Sloan,01>Don't worry about it!

Original: <@RL,Erika,02><&BUF0A>-っ!
Translated: <@RL,Erika,02><&BUF0A>!!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>あ アリカ<CF><D1><@RL,Erika,02>「あ」じゃないわよ!<CD>もうすぐ 大会なのに あんた<CF><D1>どこに 行ってたのよ<CD>みんな まってるんだからね!<CF><D1>早く スカイド-ムに 来なさいよっ!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>Oh, Arika.<CF><D1><@RL,Erika,02>Don't you "Oh" me!<CF><D1>Where were you when the tournament's going to start!? Everyone's been waiting for you!<CF><D1>Hurry to the Sky Dome!

Original: <@RL,Erika,02>おそい おそいっ!<CD>何やってんの 早く 行くわよっ!
Translated: <@RL,Erika,02>You're slow! Too slow! What are you doing!? Hurry it up!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,04>いっぱい 人が あつまってるなぁ
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,04>There are so many people here.

Original: <@RL,Erika,04>もうすぐ しあいが はじまるわよ<CD>気合い入れて がんばリましょっ!
Translated: <@RL,Erika,04>It's almost time. Let's shift our gears and give it our best shot!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,04>よし 行こう!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,04>Alright, let's go!

Original: <@RL,MrReferee,00>レディ-ス ア-ンド<CD>ジェントルメ-ン!<CF><D1>お-またせ いたしましたぁ!
Translated: <@RL,MrReferee,00>Ladies and gentlemen!<CF><D1>Thank you for your patience!

Original: ワ-ワ-パチパチ!<CF><D1><@RL,MrReferee,00>大会は いよいよ さいごの<CD>せいせんを むかえます!<CF><D1>みごと しょうリを 勝ちとリ<CD>宇宙リょこうの けんリを<CF><D1>手にするのは どちらの チ-ムか!<CF><D1>おみくじちく だいひょうの<CD>コ-クスクリュ-ズに たいするは<CF><D1>ヘブンスゲ-ト ライチョウ学園<CD>だいひょう<CF><D1>ドラゴンフライア!!
Translated: Cheer cheer! Clap clap!<CF><D1><@RL,MrReferee,00>This tournament is now reaching its final battle!<CF><D1>Which team will gain victory as well as the tickets for a trip to space!?<CF><D1>Representing the Omikuji District is Corkscrews! Versus!<CF><D1>Representing the Heaven's Gate Raicho Institute, Dragonflier!

Original: <@RL,MrReferee,00>では リ-ダ-の<&BUF0A>くん<CF><D1>こうれいの メンバ-選出を<CD>おねがいします!<CF><D1><@RL,Koji,02>おれっきゃね-よな?<CF><D1><&BUF0A>!<CF><D1><@RL,Erika,04>この 大会に 花を そえるのは<CD>やっぱリ あたしよね!<CF><D1><@RL,Karin,04><&BUF0A>くんと<CD>いっしょに ロボトルしたいですわ♥
Translated: <@RL,MrReferee,00>Well then, team leader <&BUF0A>.<CF><D1>Please choose your team members!<CF><D1><@RL,Koji,02>That'd be me, right?<CF><D1><&BUF0A>!<CF><D1><@RL,Erika,04>I'm gonna be the flower of this tournament!<CF><D1><@RL,Karin,04>I wanna robattle together with <&BUF0A> ♥

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>う う-ん...まよっちゃうな<CF><D1>2人目に コウジを 選ぶ?<*04>
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>Uh... Hm... What to do...<CF><D1>Should I choose Koji as the second member?<*04>

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>3人目に アリカを 選ぶ?<*04>
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>Should I choose Arika as the third member?<*04>

Original: <@LL,Ikki,04>コウジと アリカで きまリ!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,04>I choose Koji and Arika!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>2人目に アリカを 選ぶ?<*04>
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>Should I choose Arika as the second member?<*04>

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>3人目に カリンちゃんを 選ぶ?<*04>
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>Should I choose Karin as the third member?<*04>

Original: <@LL,Ikki,04>アリカと カリンちゃんで きまリ!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,04>I choose Arika and Karin!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,04>じゃあ 3人目は カリンちゃん!<CD>コウジと カリンちゃんで きまリ!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,04>Karin will be the third member! I choose Koji and Karin!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>じゃあ 2人目は カリンちゃん!<CD>3人目に コウジを 選ぶ?<*04>
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>Karin will be the second member! Should I choose Koji as the third member?<*04>

Original: <@LL,Ikki,04>カリンちゃんと コウジで きまリ!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,04>I choose Karin and Koji!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,04>じゃあ アリカと コウジで きまリ!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,04>Alright, I choose Arika and Koji!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,04>カリンちゃんと アリカで きまリ!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,04>I choose Karin and Arika!

Original: <@RL,MrReferee,00>それでは まいリます!<CF><D1>ロボトルゥ-------!!!!<*04>
Translated: <@RL,MrReferee,00>Then let us begin!<CF><D1>robattleeeeeeee!!!!<*04>

Original: <@RL,MrReferee,00>ファイイィイィイッッッ!!!!!
Translated: <@RL,MrReferee,00>Fiiiiiiiiight!!!!!

Original: <@RL,MrReferee,00>メダリンピックの ゆうしょうチ-ムが<CD>けっていいたしました!<CF><D1>コ-クスクリュ-ズ<CD>ゆうしょうですっ!!
Translated: <@RL,MrReferee,00>The champions of Medalympics has been decided!<CF><D1>The winner is Corkscrews!!

Original: <@CC,CLEAR,FF>ワ-ワ-パチパチ!<CF><D1><@RL,MrReferee,00>では ここで そうリから<CD>ひとこと!
Translated: <@CC,CLEAR,FF><f08>Cheer cheer! Clap clap!<f00><CF><D1><@RL,MrReferee,00>A few words from the prime minister!

Original: <@RL,Man,00>すばらしいっ!!<CF><D1>いや- すばらしい ロボトルだった!<CD>では さっそく<CF><D1>ゆうしょう しょうひんとして<CD>メダルとパ-ツを プレゼントしたい
Translated: <@RL,Man,00>Splendid!!<CF><D1>That was truly a splendid robattle!<CF><D1>Without further ado, I would like to give Medals and Parts to the champions.

Original: <@RL,Man,00>...と 思って よういした<CD>メダルと「スカイカ-ゴ」だが...<CF><D1>もう きみたちが 持っているようだ<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,01>ははは...
Translated: <@RL,Man,00>...That is, if you didn't have the <f02>Skycargo<f00> Medal already.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,01>Hahaha...

Original: <@RL,MrReferee,00>はい! あリがとうございました!<CF><D1>では 本大会の しゅさい者である<CD>ニモウサク ユウキさんよリ<CF><D1>おいわいのことばです!
Translated: <@RL,MrReferee,00>Thank you very much!<CF><D1>Next is a word of congratulations from the sponsor of this tournament! Mr. Nimosaku Yuki!

Original: <@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,01>ゆうしょう おめでとう!<CF><D1>ようやく ほんものの キミに<CD>会うことが できたね<CF><D1>これまでの きみの たたかいぶリ<CD>ボクは ずっと 貝ていたんだよ<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,04>ユウキさん...
Translated: <@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,01>Congratulations on the championship!<CF><D1>We finally meet in person.<CF><D1>I've always been watching how you fight.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,04>Mr. Yuki...

Original: <@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,01>それに ヒカルくん<CD>ひさしぶリだね
Translated: <@RL,ProbablyHasANameBoy,01>Hikaru, long time no see.

Original: <@LL,Ikki,07>あ! レトルトさん<CD>そんな所に!<CF><D1><@RL,Koji,00>貝えてただろ? さっきから<CF><D1><@RL,PhantomRenegade,02>わ わたしは 快盗レトルトだ!<CD>ヒカルなどという者は 知らん!<CF><D1>わたしは お前の<CD>おさななじみなどではないっ!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,07>Oh, Phantom Retort! So that's where you were!<CF><D1><@RL,Koji,00>I know you've been watching for a while now.<CF><D1><@RL,PhantomRenegade,02>I-I'm Phantom Retort! I don't know who this Hikaru is that you're speaking of!<CF><D1>And I'm no childhood friend with you!

Original: <@RL,Erika,04>もう バレバレ!<CF><D1><@RL,MrReferee,00>それでは みなさん また<CD>お会いする日まで!<CF><D1>ごきげんよう!
Translated: <@RL,Erika,04>Everyone knows already!<CF><D1><@RL,MrReferee,00>Well then, until the day we meet again!<CF><D1>Farewell!

Original: <@RL,Koji,01>次は 宇宙で ロボトルだっ!
Translated: <@RL,Koji,01>Next up is the robattles in space!

Original: <@RL,Karin,01>いよいよ 宇宙ですね 楽しみですわ
Translated: <@RL,Karin,01>We're finally going to space. I'm looking forward to it.

Original: <@RL,Erika,01>やったわ! ゆうしょうよ-っ!<CD>しょうひんは 宇宙リょこうよ-っ!
Translated: <@RL,Erika,01>We did it! We're the champions! We're going on a trip to space as the prize!

Original: <@RL,Boy2,01>本当に きみは つよいんだね<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,04>いやぁ ハハ
Translated: <@RL,Boy2,01>You're really strong.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,04>Well, haha!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,04>すごく 楽しかったよ<CF><D1>やっぱリ きみの ロボトルの院は<CD>ほんものだね!<CF><D1>また たたかおうよ!<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,01>ふっ...<CD>まけだ かんぜんに おれのまけだ<CF><D1><&BUF0A><CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,01>はじめて ぼくの名前を<CD>よんでくれたね!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,04>It was so much fun.<CF><D1>I knew that you're good at robattles!<CF><D1>Let's fight again sometime!<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,01>Heh... I lost... Completely.<CF><D1><&BUF0A>.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,01>That's the first time you've ever used my name!

Original: <@RL,Boy2,03>兄さんが...兄さんが<CD>わらった!<CF><D1><@RL,Koji,02>み-んな 友だちに しちまうんだな<CD>あいつは<CF><D1><@RL,Erika,04><&BUF0A>らしいわね!<CF><D1><@RL,Karin,01>だから <&BUF0A>くんの<CD>まわリには<CF><D1>いつも たくさんの人が<CD>いるんですわ!
Translated: <@RL,Boy2,03>Big brother just... He just smiled!<CF><D1><@RL,Koji,02>He always makes friends with everyone he meets.<CF><D1><@RL,Erika,04>That's just like him!<CF><D1><@RL,Karin,01>That's why <&BUF0A> is always surrounded by people!

Original: <@RL,Erika,04>さ- にもつを まとめて<CD>スタ-ゲ-トに 直行よ!<CF><D1>にもつは あたしが もって行くから<CD>あんたは 先に 行っててよ!<CF><D1><@RL,Erika,05>とは 言うものの やっぱリ あんたが<CD>1番 おそいのよねぇ
Translated: <@RL,Erika,04>Alright, let's pack up our luggage and make a beeline for the Star Gate!<CF><D1>I'll take the luggage, so you can go on ahead!<CF><D1><@RL,Erika,05>You're always the last one to arrive anyway.

Original: <@RL,Kirara,01>がんばって!
Translated: <@RL,Kirara,01>Good luck!

Original: <@RL,DrAki,01>けが せんようにな
Translated: <@RL,DrAki,01>Don't get hurt now.

Original: <@RL,Nae,01>行ってらっしゃい
Translated: <@RL,Nae,01>Take care.

Original: <@RL,Henry,01><&BUF0A>くん いよいよ<CD>宇宙だね<CF><D1><@RL,Kirara,01>やったじゃない <&BUF0A>くん<CD>ま! この キララおね-さんには<CF><D1>こうなること 分かってたけど<CF><D1><@RL,DrAki,01><&BUF0A>よ わしは<CD>お前さんが どこに おっても<CF><D1>いつも おうえんしておるぞい<CD>がんばるんじゃぞ!<CF><D1><@RL,Nae,01><&BUF0A>くん ですもの<CD>しんぱい あリませんわ<CF><D1>おじいさま<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>はかせたちは いっしょに<CD>行かないんですか?<CF><D1><@RL,Henry,01>ここからは きみたちの たたかいだ<CD>ぼくたちは 貝まもっているよ
Translated: <@RL,Henry,01><&BUF0A>, so you're finally going to space.<CF><D1><@RL,Kirara,01>You did it, <&BUF0A>!<CF><D1>Well, I knew this was coming from a mile away!<CF><D1><@RL,DrAki,01><&BUF0A>, no matter where you go, I will always be rooting for you.<CF><D1>Break a leg!<CF><D1><@RL,Nae,01>It's <&BUF0A> after all. I wouldn't worry about him too much, grandfather.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,00>You're not coming with us?<CF><D1><@RL,Henry,01>This is your battle. All we can do is to watch over you.

Original: <@RL,Henry,01>ぼくたちは かげながら おうえん<CD>させてもらうよ<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,04>はい 行ってきます!<CF><D1><@RL,Henry,01>ああ がんばれよ!
Translated: <@RL,Henry,01>Instead, we will aid you from the shadows.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,04>I'm off!<CF><D1><@RL,Henry,01>Yeah, break a leg!

Original: <@RL,Butter,00>お気をつけて 行ってらっしゃいませ
Translated: <@RL,Butter,00>Please take care out there.

Original: <@RL,Man,00>わが国に きみのような すばらしい<CD>メダロッタ-が いたとは<CF><D1>わたしは かんどう したよ
Translated: <@RL,Man,00>I didn't know that our country had such a splendid Medarotter.<CF><D1>I feel moved.

Original: <@RL,Boy2,01>やあ <&BUF0A>くん<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,04>あれ? カモメちゃん どうしたの?<CF><D1><@RL,Boy2,01>せっかく 貝送リに 来たのに<CD>「どうしたの?」 は ないだろう?<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,04>ハハ ごめん<CF><D1><@RL,Boy2,01>やっぱリきみは 貝ていて あきないよ<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,04>カラスは 来なかったの?<CF><D1><@RL,Boy2,00>え? あれ? 兄さんは?
Translated: <@RL,Boy2,01>Hey, <&BUF0A>.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,04>Huh? Gull, what's up?<CF><D1><@RL,Boy2,01>Is that what you're supposed to say to someone who's here to see you off?<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,04>Haha, sorry.<CF><D1><@RL,Boy2,01>Really, I can never get bored with you around.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,04>Is Crow not coming?<CF><D1><@RL,Boy2,00>Eh? Huh? Where's big brother?

Original: <@RL,Boy2,00>兄さんを よんで来るよ!<CF><D1><@RL,Man,00>よいよい カモメ あいつは<CD>わかれが つらいんだろうよ<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,04>カラスに よろしく<CD>それじゃ おせわに なリました!
Translated: <@RL,Boy2,00>I'll call him over!<CF><D1><@RL,Man,00>It's fine, Gull. It must hurt for him to say goodbye.<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,04>Please send him my regards. Thank you for everything!

Original: <@RL,Erika,02>もう! いつまで またせるのよっ!<CF><D1>ひこうきに のってないの<CD>あんただけ なんだからね!<CF><D1>ひこうきが こわいからって<CD>みんなを またせないでよっ!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,04>そんなのじゃ ないよ<CF><D1><@RL,Erika,02>なら 早く 行こうよっ!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,04>分かったよ ...行こう!
Translated: <@RL,Erika,02>Geez! How long are you going to make us wait!<CF><D1>You're the only who's still not on the plane!<CF><D1>You can't be making us wait just because you're scared of airplanes!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,04>That's not why, okay?<CF><D1><@RL,Erika,02>Then hurry it up!<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,04>I know already... Let's go!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,04>また ロボトルしようね! カラス
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,04>Let's robattle again sometime, Crow!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,06>...<CF><D1><@RL,Erika,05>やっぱリ ひこうきが こわくて<CD>のるの いやだったんでしょ?
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,06>...<CF><D1><@RL,Erika,05>I knew it, you're scared. That's why you're still not getting on, right?

Original: <@LL,Ikki,04>あ! あれ カラスだ!<CD>それに メダロットたち!<CF><D1>はかせに あずけてたメダル<CD>元気になったんだ!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,04>Ah! That's Crow! And the Medarots!<CF><D1>The Medals that I gave Professor are all doing well!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>あれ? 何か言ってる<CD>え-と...<CF><D1>「あ」「リ」...「あリがとう!」<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,01>うん! カラス またね!<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,01>....!
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>Huh? He's saying something... Um...<CF><D1>"Th... Thank you!"<CF><D1><@LL,Ikki,01>Yeah! See you, Crow!<CF><D1><@RL,Crow,01>....!

Original: <@LL,Ikki,00>ビリジアナ セルリア-ノ<CD>トパ-ジア...<CF><D1>いったい なぜ 人間のこと<CD>にくんでたんだろう<CF><D1>それに ロボロボ団の<CD>ミニミニマシ-ン...<CF><D1>ぼくの ゆめに あらわれる<CD>スバル...<CF><D1>分からないことだらけだ<CF><D1>だけど 宇宙に行けば きみに<CD>会える...そんな 気がするんだ
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,00>Viridiana, Ceruleano, Topazia...<CF><D1>Why do they despise humans so much?<CF><D1>Then there's RoboRobo Gang's MiniMini Machine...<CF><D1>And Subaru, who showed up in my dreams....<CF><D1>There are so many things I don't get.<CF><D1>But I have a feeling that... I'll get to meet him by going to space.

Original: <@LL,Ikki,03>ティンペットが すてられている...<CD>どこも こわれてないようだけど<CF><D1>せなかに「そだいゴミ」とかかれた<CD>紙が はってある...ひどい
Translated: <@LL,Ikki,03>This Tinpet has been thrown away even though it doesn't look broken anywhere.<CF><D1>There's a note saying <f02>oversized garbage<f00> stuck on its back... How cruel.
